cu.explanation_en: Setting phy_log_level to an invalid value will cause PHY layer logging configuration errors and prevent proper PHY event logging.

du.explanation_en: Setting phy_log_level to an invalid value will cause PHY layer logging configuration errors and prevent proper PHY event logging.
du.explanation_zh: 將 phy_log_level 設定為無效值會導致 PHY 層日誌配置錯誤，並阻止正確的 PHY 事件記錄。
